advice_english: Plant maize and teff this season for optimal yields. Apply organic fertilizer before planting.
advice_amharic: በዚህ ወቅት በቆሎ እና ጤፍ ለተሻለ ምርት ይዝራ። ከመዝራት በፊት የተፈጥሮ ማዳበሪያ ይተግብሩ።
advice_afaan_oromo: Yeroo kana boqqolloo fi xaafii oomisha gaariif facaasaa. Osoo hin facaasin dura xurii uumamaa fayyadamaa.
